about.summary: Library for working with HTML/CSS color formats in Python.

name: webcolors
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.5" %}

package:
  name: webcolors
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: webcolors-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/w/webcolors/webcolors-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: 2e9da1bbb7a087c6108e05be64640afb

build:
  number: 2
  script: python setup.py install

requirements:
  build:
    - python

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - webcolors

about:
  home: https://github.com/ubernostrum/webcolors
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Library for working with HTML/CSS color formats in Python.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
